title: Monkey dressed up in a costume gets its comeuppance
text: comments A monkey who was wearing a bizarre costume had to go on the defensive after a feisty chihuahua bit back when it nuzzled on its whiskers. In the strange video, the animal can be seen scratching the dog while it was sat down on a sofa. The monkey then started to use its teeth to gently chew on the dog's face - which resulted in the chihuahua becoming more agitated. The monkey was wearing a bizarre outfit when it started to scratch the chihuahua which was sitting on the sofa Just seconds later, the dog showed its small but sharp teeth and quickly turned to the right and tried to bite the monkey. The animal was knocked over after the dog reacted in a fierce manner and was forced to retreat after the pet had a second bite. RELATED ARTICLES
